      <T n="text">0xF146C5F4<!--String: "As Sims progress through the Noble career, they will gain access to Noble Titles that show their status within the Kingdom.\n\nNoble Titles can be inherited by Sims who are not in the Noble Career through marriage or birth. If a Sim has a title from both the Noble Career and an inherited title, the higher rank Title will be used. Noble Titles can be found in a Sim's Career Panel and show how the title was inherited.\n\nA Noble can <b><font color='#199C2C'>promise their Noble Title inheritance</font></b> to their children or spouse to continue their legacy. To be eligible for title inheritance Sims must be Teens or older and in the Noble Career, then upon the death or abdication of the Noble they will level up to their rank automatically. Sims will lose any promised inheritance if they leave the Noble Career or move worlds."--></T>
    </U>
